{"tid":1665893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一班學生自己搞咗個幫助貧窮小朋友／學生計劃","createTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T17:38:02.000Z","uid":238660,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9734cd0171303082928d3e3127880ec327c17a8f","tid":1665893,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:00.000Z","msg":"一定有好多人問點解你要去開多一個Channel ，周圍都有好多人做緊，你做咩又去開多一個。<br />\n<br />\n係咁嘅，因為就算有好多人做緊，但係都會有小朋友獲得唔到協助，而且早排都有好多唔同嘅手足聯絡我，希望可以幫到佢日常生活 最基本食飯 搭車 ，咁我都會問返身邊朋友，睇下有冇人可以幫下手。都希望可以盡快幫助佢哋，但係要幫手嘅手足越來越多，好真心講句我哋都幫唔到幾多，有就幫冇就幫你諗辦法。<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋先想喺度希望大家，如果可以有唔同嘅物資捐出嚟，就聯絡我哋，只要你有咩想幫到佢哋，我哋都會盡力交到佢哋手上。<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hongkong1021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhongkong1021&d=g2FbBnZIPvId2LkE7nNtja0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=98b88f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hongkong1021</a>"},{"pid":"f496434ccb271b55958068799e79f9c5b330aa04","tid":1665893,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"ccfa6a0c69345b7fafbdc096dc8450d1929f00a2","tid":1665893,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:37.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"3b8e393d9761130abf4bffdf994c43fe13a86c34","tid":1665893,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:47.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"7121075faa5d4f4ba0100f8bbd6e5bd95e8d99ce","tid":1665893,"uid":82955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T17:36:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1665303/page/1</a><br />\n[文宣升級] 郵差叔叔送信純熟將文宣迅速送出!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4H03stW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4H03stW.png&h=37a4782b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2df106879e981534ec21c960270a649c24b3bd9","tid":1665893,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike"